```css
/* Variables de la app (en body.appNN) */
body.myapp {
  --myapp-endcap-w: clamp(1.875rem, 5.25vw, 5rem);
  --myapp-endcap-h: clamp(3.8rem, 4vw, 4.75rem);
}

/* Endcaps amarillos rectangulares en los extremos de la timeline.
   `inset: auto` cancela el inset: 0 heredado del modo circular del
   app-common, que de lo contrario haría que `right: 0` quedara ignorado. */
body[data-visual="nuzic"].myapp
  .timeline-wrapper:has(.timeline):not(:has(.soundline-container))
  .timeline::before,
body[data-visual="nuzic"].myapp
  .timeline-wrapper:has(.timeline):not(:has(.soundline-container))
  .timeline::after {
  content: '';
  display: block;
  position: absolute;
  inset: auto;
  opacity: 1;
  border: 0;
  top: 0%;
  width: var(--myapp-endcap-w);
  height: var(--myapp-endcap-h);
  background: var(--nuzic-yellow);
  border-radius: 4px;
  z-index: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.timeline::before { left: 0;  transform: translateX(calc(-100% - 1.25rem)); }
.timeline::after  { right: 0; transform: translateX(calc(100% + 1.25rem)); }
```

El `translateX(calc(-100% - 1.25rem))` proyecta el endcap fuera del `.timeline` (que tiene `margin: 20px auto` heredado de app-common). El extra 1.25rem compensa esos 20px del cream box-shadow.

```css
/* App-level variables (on body.appNN) */
body.myapp {
  --myapp-endcap-w: clamp(1.875rem, 5.25vw, 5rem);
  --myapp-endcap-h: clamp(3.8rem, 4vw, 4.75rem);
}

/* Yellow rectangular endcaps at the timeline edges.
   `inset: auto` cancels the inset:0 inherited from circular mode (otherwise
   `right: 0` would be ignored as the box becomes over-constrained). */
body[data-visual="nuzic"].myapp
  .timeline-wrapper:has(.timeline):not(:has(.soundline-container))
  .timeline::before,
body[data-visual="nuzic"].myapp
  .timeline-wrapper:has(.timeline):not(:has(.soundline-container))
  .timeline::after {
  content: '';
  display: block;
  position: absolute;
  inset: auto;
  opacity: 1;
  border: 0;
  top: 0%;
  width: var(--myapp-endcap-w);
  height: var(--myapp-endcap-h);
  background: var(--nuzic-yellow);
  border-radius: 4px;
  z-index: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.timeline::before { left: 0;  transform: translateX(calc(-100% - 1.25rem)); }
.timeline::after  { right: 0; transform: translateX(calc(100% + 1.25rem)); }
```

The `translateX(calc(-100% - 1.25rem))` projects each endcap outside the `.timeline` (which has `margin: 20px auto` inherited from app-common). The extra 1.25rem compensates for those 20px of cream box-shadow.

```css
/* Fons de la timeline: gradient vertical amb franja groga intensa
   centrada-baixa, sobre la línia dels ::after ticks dels pulse-numbers. */
body[data-visual="nuzic"].myapp
  .timeline-wrapper:has(.timeline):not(:has(.soundline-container))
  .timeline {
  background:
    linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      var(--nuzic-yellow-light) 0,
      var(--nuzic-yellow-light) 70%,
      var(--nuzic-yellow) 70%,
      var(--nuzic-yellow) 93%,
      var(--nuzic-yellow-light) 93%,
      var(--nuzic-yellow-light) 100%
    );
}
```

Els stops 70%/93% mantenen la franja sempre alineada visualment amb els ticks `::after`, independentment de l'alçada concreta de la timeline (que pot variar segons `clamp(3.8rem, 4vw, 4.75rem)` del viewport).

```css
/* Wrapper del fraction-editor. `gap: 0` aquí es no-op para variant simple
   (no hay ghost-fraction), pero es seguro mantener. */
.fraction-editor-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  gap: 0;
}

/* Rectángulo vertical amarillo. `left: calc(-W)` lo alinea con el endcap
   izquierdo de la timeline (apps standalone). En apps plano-2D: left: 0. */
.fraction-editor {
  position: relative;
  left: calc(0px - var(--myapp-endcap-w));
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: stretch;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 0.2rem;
  width: var(--myapp-endcap-w);
  box-sizing: border-box;
  padding: 0.5rem 0;
  border: 3px solid var(--nuzic-yellow);
  border-radius: 0.4rem;
  color: #000;
}

.fraction-editor .top,
.fraction-editor .bottom {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

/* Barra de la fracción: border-bottom de `.top` con ancho parcial.
   Solo válido para simple (un solo spinner visible). En complex usar pseudo. */
.fraction-editor .top {
  border-bottom: 4px solid #000;
  width: 65%;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Números en negro puro, font-weight 900 */
.fraction-editor input {
  width: 100%;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.8vw, 2.7rem);
  background: none;
  border: none;
  color: #000 !important;
  font-family: 'Ubuntu', sans-serif;
  outline: none;
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1;
  padding: 0;
}

/* Override del 0.5 opacity por defecto del input readonly */
.fraction-editor input:disabled,
.fraction-editor input:read-only {
  opacity: 1 !important;
  cursor: default !important;
  color: #000 !important;
}
```

