The `var(--myapp-endcap-w)` margins are critical: they reserve horizontal space for the `::before` (left endcap, projected via `translateX(calc(-100% - 1.25rem))`) and `::after` (right endcap, `translateX(calc(100% + 1.25rem))`). Without these margins the endcaps would project outside the viewport and be clipped.

